<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 2: WHY THIS AREA
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Established living with consistent inner-south demand.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Greenslopes is a well-established inner-south suburb with strong owner-occupier appeal, good access to the CBD and Coorparoo, and a consistent buyer base drawn to its affordability relative to the surrounding inner suburbs.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I understand the buyer profile active in Greenslopes and the broader inner-south market. I build campaigns that connect with that audience and create the competition that drives the best results.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Greenslopes Private Hospital on Logan Road is one of Brisbane's largest private hospitals and acts as an employment anchor that drives consistent demand from medical professionals seeking nearby housing. Logan Road itself is undergoing a slow but visible gentrification, with new cafes and small restaurants replacing older retail uses and slowly shifting buyers' perceptions of the suburb's identity. The streets running up the ridge toward Holland Park attract buyers who want a quieter residential address within 6km of the CBD, and those properties have been consistently achieving strong auction results. Demand from buyers priced out of Coorparoo and East Brisbane has strengthened Greenslopes' buyer pool over the past two years.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Greenslopes Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Inner South Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Established Suburb</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Consistent owner-occupier demand</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/woolloongabba" style="color:#c4912a;">Woolloongabba</a>, <a href="/suburbs/coorparoo" style="color:#c4912a;">Coorparoo</a>, <a href="/suburbs/holland-park" style="color:#c4912a;">Holland Park</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
