        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Greenslopes' median house price is approximately $1.1 million as of early 2026. The suburb offers a practical inner-city lifestyle with multiple bus routes, proximity to the PA Hospital and a mix of character homes and post-war properties at relatively accessible pricing.</p>
      </details>

